  "description": "<p>小灵通将于今年9月底正式退市。记者了解到，强制退市所带来的设备更换费用，是小灵通用户不满的重要原因。<strong>对此，小灵通用户的利益诉求集中于一点，即要求 运营商对强制退市进行合理补偿，维护小灵通用户的合法权益。他们认为：“不能增加消费者的额外负担，不能让消费者为运营商的历史过错买单。”</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2f1711ff/sc/34/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245878.htm&amp;t=%E8%81%94%E9%80%9A%E7%A7%B0%E5%B0%8F%E7%81%B5%E9%80%9A9%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%BC%BA%E5%88%B6%E9%80%80%E5%B8%82+%E8%BD%AC%E7%BD%91%E6%97%A0%E8%A1%A5%E5%81%BF%E5%BC%95%E4%BA%89%E8%AE%AE\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245878.htm&amp;t=%E8%81%94%E9%80%9A%E7%A7%B0%E5%B0%8F%E7%81%B5%E9%80%9A9%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%BC%BA%E5%88%B6%E9%80%80%E5%B8%82+%E8%BD%AC%E7%BD%91%E6%97%A0%E8%A1%A5%E5%81%BF%E5%BC%95%E4%BA%89%E8%AE%AE\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245878.htm&amp;t=%E8%81%94%E9%80%9A%E7%A7%B0%E5%B0%8F%E7%81%B5%E9%80%9A9%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%BC%BA%E5%88%B6%E9%80%80%E5%B8%82+%E8%BD%AC%E7%BD%91%E6%97%A0%E8%A1%A5%E5%81%BF%E5%BC%95%E4%BA%89%E8%AE%AE\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245878.htm&amp;t=%E8%81%94%E9%80%9A%E7%A7%B0%E5%B0%8F%E7%81%B5%E9%80%9A9%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%BC%BA%E5%88%B6%E9%80%80%E5%B8%82+%E8%BD%AC%E7%BD%91%E6%97%A0%E8%A1%A5%E5%81%BF%E5%BC%95%E4%BA%89%E8%AE%AE\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"ht